    "Right: the user distribution over familiesstage, the Self-Teaching is the most popular among our three main functions.",
    "Its corresponding Gloss Correction interface was invoked more than 50% when a user used our APP.",
    "Some user feedback indicates that signs users believed to be correct were classified as incorrect.",
    "Upon review, the success retrieval rate of the self-teaching feature during testing should be no less than 90% accurate.",
    "Some of the errors reported in user feedback were due to the diversity of sign language leading to retrieval failures, while others were caused by users not noticing subtle differences between different signs."
